# Input

```yml
%TAG ! tag:clarkevans.com,2002:
--- !shape
  # Use the ! handle for presenting
  # tag:clarkevans.com,2002:circle
- !circle
  center: &ORIGIN {x: 73, y: 129}
  radius: 7
- !line
  start: *ORIGIN
  finish: { x: 89, y: 102 }
- !label
  start: *ORIGIN
  color: 0xFFEEBB
  text: Pretty vector drawing.

```


# Prettier differences

```diff
--- Prettier
+++ Biome
@@ -1,6 +1,5 @@
 %TAG ! tag:clarkevans.com,2002:
----
-!shape
+--- !shape
 # Use the ! handle for presenting
 # tag:clarkevans.com,2002:circle
 - !circle
```

# Output

```yml
%TAG ! tag:clarkevans.com,2002:
--- !shape
# Use the ! handle for presenting
# tag:clarkevans.com,2002:circle
- !circle
  center: &ORIGIN { x: 73, y: 129 }
  radius: 7
- !line
  start: *ORIGIN
  finish: { x: 89, y: 102 }
- !label
  start: *ORIGIN
  color: 0xFFEEBB
  text: Pretty vector drawing.
```
